  "steps": [
    "Heat 2 tablespoons ghee in a pan, add onions, garlic, ginger, cashewnuts, green chillies and coriander stems, mix and sauté till onions are translucent.",
    "Transfer the mixture onto a plate and allow to cool completely.",
    "Transfer the mixture into a grinder jar, add mint leaves, coriander leaves and yogurt and grind to fine paste.",
    "Heat 2 tablespoons ghee in another pan, add cinnamon and black peppercorns, mix and sauté till fragrant.",
    "Add ground paste, coriander powder and ¼ teaspoon turmeric powder and cook on medium heat for 8-10 minutes.",
    "Meanwhile score the eggs. Heat 2 tablespoons ghee in a shallow non-stick pan, add eggs, remaining turmeric powder and red chilli powder and sauté till golden brown. Drain and set aside.",
    "Add salt and 1½ cups water to the gravy, mix well and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Pour the gravy into a serving plate/ bowl. Arrange eggs on top and serve hot."
